<item>
            <title>[LU-9778] ll_read_ahead_pages no longer returns count of pages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9778</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7990&quot; title=&quot; Large bulk IO support&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7990&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7990&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; clio: revise readahead to support 16MB IO&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    The major work is to adjust read ahead policy to issue&lt;br/&gt;
    read ahead RPC by underlying RPC size&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Test case is backport from Andrew Perepechko&apos;s&lt;br/&gt;
    &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7140&quot; title=&quot;Few 4 MB BRW rpcs from readahead path&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7140&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7140&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: too few 4 MiB RPCs from readahead&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/16374&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/16374&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Signed-off-by: Jinshan Xiong &amp;lt;jinshan.xiong@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    Signed-off-by: Gu Zheng &amp;lt;gzheng@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    Change-Id: Ib25ff37712389cca7fcee86996124e7c9dd4ec9a&lt;br/&gt;
    Reviewed-on: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/19368&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/19368&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Removed &apos;count&apos; from ll_read_ahead_pages, meaning it no longer returns the # of pages read.  Several debug statements still try to print out # of pages read ahead, but can&apos;t.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
